   "source": [
    "# 🤖 CS Algorithm Q&A Assistant — Inference Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "Loads the fine-tuned model and runs a Flask API + Gradio interface.\n",
    "\n",
    "## ⚠️ Before Running\n",
    "- Set Runtime to **GPU T4** in Colab\n",
    "- Make sure `final_model.zip` is in your Google Drive at `MyDrive/cs_algo_assistant/`\n",
    "- Add your ngrok authtoken from dashboard.ngrok.com\n",
    "\n",
    "## 🌐 After Running\n",
    "- Flask API will be live at your ngrok URL\n",
    "- Your Vercel website at cs-algo-assistant.vercel.app will automatically connect"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Cell 1 — Mount Google Drive\n",
    "from google.colab import drive\n",
    "drive.mount('/content/drive')\n",
    "print('✅ Drive mounted!')"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
